[[Image:Map of Podsused-Vrapče District (Zagreb).svg|thumb|right|Podsused – Vrapče as a part of [[Zagreb]]]]
'''Podsused – Vrapče''' is one of the districts of [[Zagreb]], [[Croatia]]. It is located in the north-western part of the city. In 2011, the district had 45,759 inhabitants.<ref>{{Croatian Census 2011|url=http://www.dzs.hr/Eng/censuses/census2011/results/htm/e01_01_01_cet/E01_01_01_zup21_cet.html|title=Population by Age and Sex, by Districts of City of Zagreb, 2011 Census}}</ref> Its area is 36.188 km<sup>2</sup>.<ref name="zagreb.hr">{{cite web|url=http://www.zagreb.hr/default.aspx?id=13421|title=Osnovni podaci|language=Croatian|work=zagreb.hr|accessdate=2013-11-24}}</ref>

==List of neighborhoods in Podsused – Vrapče==
* [[Vrapče, Zagreb|Vrapče]]
* [[Susedgrad]]
* [[Podsused]]
* Gajnice
* [[Gornji Stenjevec]]

